title: [HorribleSubs] Yamada-kun and the Seven Witches - 08 [1080p].mkv
description: One day, high-school boy Yamada bumps into the beautiful girl Shiraishi on the stairs (literally), and their lips touch as they fall. When they regain their wits, they realize that they have swapped bodies. As time progresses, the two realize that this is not the only mysterious happening in the school. Source: ANN Note: The first episode was pre-aired at a special event on 14.03.2015. Regular broadcast started on April 12, 2015
